column2: SELECT      s.specObjID,   s.ra,    s.dec,   s.z,   s.class,    s.subclass,   s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.run2d,   e.lgm_tot_p5#,   zoo.p_mg  FROM specObjAll AS s   JOIN galSpecExtra AS e ON s.specObjID = e.specObjID   JOIN zooSpec AS zoo ON s.specObjID = zoo.specObjID   WHERE  -- (e.bptclass = #) AND  -- (e.lgm_tot_p5# >= #) AND   (zoo.p_mg BETWEEN # AND #) AND   (s.z <= #) AND   (s.class = &&& AND s.subclass = &&&) OR    (s.class = &&& AND s.subclass = &&&)    order by zoo.p_mg
